	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On the RGB PPU, the tint bits force a particular component to 100% brightness instead of slightly darkening the other two components. Just Breed and <a href="http://www.digitpress.com/forum/archive/index.php/t-147009.html" class="postlink">a few other games</a> will show a white screen on a Famicom Titler or any other FC or NES with an RGB PPU.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


