		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">DaddyLongLegs wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">To be fair, I recently got my AV Famicom RGB modded, and it looks 20x better on my plasma than when using composite. It's using s-video (240p works fine over s-video) but the picture is so much better it's ridiculous.<br /><br />I actually really like the different pallet. Only instance in where it was bizarre was in Super Mario Bros 2 (USA), the snow world (world 4) was purple instead of blue. But if you look on the back of the box for the game, it shows up purple so meh!</div>
